Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:42.86,Default,gio,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Najdeš ho jen na konci dlouhé, tvrdé cesty...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:44.32,Default,gio,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Romeo.{\i0}
